DOCUMENTS REQUIRED
=============================

Required documents include 10th class marks memo, 12th/Intermediate marks memo, Transfer Certificate (TC), Aadhaar card, and entrance examination rank card (if applicable). Application confirmation is sent via registered email, and updates are communicated through phone and email.

