=============================
ACCREDITATION & APPROVALS
=============================
Vignan's Lara Institute of Technology & Science (VLITS) is approved by the All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE) and affiliated to Jawaharlal Nehru Technological University, Kakinada (JNTUK). The institution has been accredited with an 'A+' grade by NAAC and has NBA accreditation for select engineering programs.

